v 1.1.1 - 1.1.6

* Props name, buttons-container-class close-button-text, buttons, close-icon-class, background-color, draggable, resizable, top-close-icon-container-class
    1. name - Unique modal name
    2. draggable - Enable draggable for the modal
    3. resizable - Enable resizable for the modal
    4. buttons-container-class - Modal bottom buttons container custom classes
    5. close-button-text - Custom text to default bottom close button
    6. buttons - Add your custom buttons to modal
    7. close-icon-class - Top modal close button icon class
    8. background-color - Add custom background color to modal this poperty accepts all color formats text, hex, rgb
    9. top-close-icon-container-class - Modal top button container custom classes
* Added ability to change background color
* Add new utils to Normalize contrast when you change background

v 1.2.0

* Added multi-window modals window functionality
* Added the ability to work with forms in a modal, now the modal will submit the form when closed
* Added closeAll method to close all already opened modals
* Added callbacks @before-open, @after-open, @before-close, @after-close, @on-submit

-- Minor changes
    1. Added custom bottom button property to set button type - type
    2. Fixed error with button when you don't pass click()
    3. Improve resize to work with multi-window modals
    4. Change default props names
        buttons-container-class > bbc-class
        close-icon-class > tci-class
        top-close-icon-container-class > tcic-class
        close-button-text > dcb-text

How to use new change you will find on doc https://lightmodal.netlify.app/guide/getting-started

v 1.2.1 - 1.2.2

!!!Critical changes

* Fix error (Module not found: Error: Can't resolve './namedColors') when you install plug-in

v 1.2.3

* Resizable logic made more intuitive
* Property ":title" finally removed from the plugin
* Refactoring code